## Design and implement core data models and API

- Design database schema for:
  - Users (roles, profile info)
  - PDRs (review period, status, timestamps)
  - Goals ("What")
  - Values/Behaviours ("How")
  - Ratings, Comments, Audit logs

- Implement backend API endpoints for:
  - CRUD for PDRs, Goals, Values, Ratings, Comments
  - Status changes (lock/unlock, check-in, review)
  - History retrieval